After a quiet day of drizzling, things are picking up rapiy. Please exercise caution and check on your friends and family to make sure they are okay.

Buckle up, it may get even crazier than this past weekend in Palo Alto where all of University Avenue was under 8 inches of brown water (which hadn't happened since 1998).
